Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}"以力量作為交換"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}"已無法得到愛情"
